author: tomdz
msg: The collection factory is now fully integrated, i.e. every collection creation during the retrieval of collections (directly or via proxy) or queries uses the collection factory

The collection factory has info about the collection descriptor for the collection and the object that will receive it (if retrieving a collection descriptor) and about the query, thus allowing for more complex collection creation
